Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:28.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽好了不要輸給老鷹和獅鷲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:30.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:32.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:33.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:37.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有那樣的事 有志者事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:40.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}重要的是幹勁 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:46.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要保重


Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:07.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天比平時都要興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:09.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能是能在這麼寬敞的地方 很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:11.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:16.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:19.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:21.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:23.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}由我來拿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.04,0:01:25.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:31.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 趁我一不注意就想接近美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:32.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這垃圾蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:33.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:38.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用在意 這也是部員的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:41.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去吧

Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:21.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}淚水色的避雨所

Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你 差不多該住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:33.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這麼問的吧 你到底打算怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這不是一直都做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:39.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的垃圾蟲居然想接近美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:41.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還早了100萬光年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:44.09,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\bord1\fscx100\fad(300,300)\c&HFFFFFF&\frz0\t(0,100,\frz360)\t(100,500,\fscx1000)\an7\pos(26,10)}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:44.09,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\bord1\fscy100\fad(300,300)\c&HFFFFFF&\frx0\t(0,100,\frx360)\t(100,500,\fscy400)\an7\pos(52,4)}|
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:44.09,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an7\fs32\fad(500,300)\pos(66,42)}科普：在儒略歷的一年的時間中　在自由空間以及距離任何引力場或磁場無限遠的地方\N　　　一光子所行走的距離 一光年等於 9,460,730,472,580,800米……\N　　　於是“光年”是距離不是時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:43.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說的是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}認真中的認真 非常認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:51.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪 你完全沒了解自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:55.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 看你過於在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:02.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}住嘴 我和原來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:05.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來是 以後還是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:12.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一起在這喝茶怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 這家咖啡館真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:24.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔非常贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們看 小熊喵也能進去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:29.92,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允許寵物\N（和寵物一起喝咖啡）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}

Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:31.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:37.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 稍微有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:18.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 發生什麼事情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你居然不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:28.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 新吾現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都已經一個星期了吧 習慣新環境了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:34.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:35.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微有點不太精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:43.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 看來是對新環境還不太適應了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:46.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能是那樣的感覺

Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真厲害 能準備這麼多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:03.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}根據動物種類的不同準備的 不知不覺就變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算這麼說 也不能就放任不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡該輪到女僕出場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:12.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之把現在不用的東西先收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就放在這個紙箱裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:19.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}賭上安潔的自尊 完美地整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我去把這個洗乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊等等 小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:29.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:33.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 這裡就交給我們收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你去幫小紗凪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的 就這麼點事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:43.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還帶有石子 水箱也很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我 讓我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:47.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:58.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 好冰涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別說這麼沒出息的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:08.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你這麼說 校舍裡也有可以出熱水的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在校舍裡 不能清洗這種會弄髒水槽的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偷偷洗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:17.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要認真遵守規則 這個是喵咪部的紀律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:20.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:36.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這傢伙 不僅是垃圾蟲 還是柔弱蟲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那真對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:03.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:06.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:08.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:13.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你莫非 就只有這麼一塊手帕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:14.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}之前借給你的也是這塊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你有清洗過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃有認真洗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我就用好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:39.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}裝太滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是箱子又只有這麼一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:48.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的 再過一會新吾就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等主人回來以後 誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:59.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}向主人拜託這樣的事情 作為女僕有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:02.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放心吧 我會拜託他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:07.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:15.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 差不多可以還給我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要消毒過後再給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是清洗才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:28.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 你看著就像養了奇怪的細菌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:29.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以要消毒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:30.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:31.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算是這樣吧

Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…

Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 美羽精神也不太好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽也…嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 新吾也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:55.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}飯也不怎麼吃 一邊在屋裡亂轉一邊哭叫著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:58.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和飼主那裡聽說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}帶去醫院看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:06.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 但是沒有發現生病或者有什麼異常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:11.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有就是那個… 有貓喜歡呆在家的說法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:16.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想著莫非是突然到了陌生的地方 變得有些混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就帶來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在找什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:27.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才就一直在房間裡轉圈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:31.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在找什麼東西嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:35.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽在找的是新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:46.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你 想見新吾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:48.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:52.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過對不起 新吾已經不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:58.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然… 美羽必須和新吾在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:06.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽也由我來負責飼養
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:08.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:10.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪已經在養新吾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:17.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽只要和新吾在一起 就全部會恢復正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:18.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去把新吾帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:22.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…

Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:38.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:45.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:48.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你清楚嗎 新吾和美羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:51.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是喜歡的人的名字和情敵的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:57.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就想一直這樣生活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:04.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的… 不是情敵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:08.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩是值得我尊敬的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:13.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了 要是這樣也就只能如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然覺得很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都說沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:55.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起這個 萬智
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也養隻貓怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:12:59.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貓可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古靈精怪隨心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:06.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然遇上不喜歡的事情馬上就逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一旦認定你了 那就已經是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你不是正好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身邊沒有男人 正好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:17.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:19.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:34.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然沒有新吾在身邊 就不會去吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:40.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩 問你一件事可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:45.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:49.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼要反對紗凪養貓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪對貓會過敏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:56.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:02.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔們在這裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:03.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:06.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:09.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就沒有問的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡的打掃中午已經做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:15.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果那樣 還為什麼一直呆在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:25.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:31.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然說是過敏 但沒有嚴重到會馬上發作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果只是在這裡照顧的話 是沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:35.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果是在家裡養的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定是在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:45.97,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以就反對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:46.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:54.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我小時候 得過小兒哮喘所以知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:15:00.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能自由呼吸至幾近窒息 無法停止咳嗽的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:05.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算知道會這樣 那傢伙還…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太過勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:15.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩也 一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:15.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:22.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在我看來 你們兩個都為了動物而做出犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:26.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒想過那是犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:34.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果那樣的話 紗凪也是一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:35.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:39.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們都是那樣的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:46.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 可能是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:52.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這房間也變得寂靜多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:57.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢 那孩子下周也應該能回歸山林了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:58.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就只剩下小熊喵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:03.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:08.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總有一天 也想讓小熊喵回歸山林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還沒有和新吾說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我和小熊喵初次相遇的事情

Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊

Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:40.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得非常地怕生 像是不願和人類有所接觸的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:46.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後… 兩年前和小熊喵再次相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:52.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個時候的小熊喵 只剩下自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和現在相比 非常地柔弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:55.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}非常地膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:56.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不停地顫抖著

Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}夢中在向母親撒嬌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或者是 在和朋友們玩耍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:16.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放心吧 不久之後一定能和它們重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:18.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小熊喵是脫離了群體的野生動物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:30.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以必須讓它回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:35.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是 喵咪部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新…新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:56.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:02.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 突然間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:11.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:15.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然間這麼說 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:19.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}選擇我可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:31.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:36.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾不是喜歡小紗凪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:40.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以… 都說那是誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:47.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:52.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 我喜歡的是美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:05.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:12.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果不介意這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:14.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:17.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯

Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:26.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…

Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被小熊喵給嚇壞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:40.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下雨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:58.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:04.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}努力讓我認可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:14.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為交換 我會叫你新吾的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:28.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你 喜歡美羽前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:10.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在做什麼呢 新吾會被淋濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:17.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:22.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是哭的話 男人是不會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:35.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有今天 可以為那傢伙而哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:43.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}忘記他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:49.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那之前 你可以在我懷裡盡情哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也有喜歡的人嗎

